S.FORM: == Alexander Lukashenko == u siwkay niza 8 bulad 30 demiad, Alexander Lukashenko, u misingkiway. 1954 a mihca nalecuhan u tabakiay a tapang(Cungtung) nu kanatal (congtung) nu Belarus ayza sa ci Alexander Lukashenko, micakat a demiad sa i 1994 a mihca 7 bulad 20 demiad. u tatama, i 1994.7 sakacacay maala ku Cungtung ciniza. 2001.9 maala aca ku Cungtung ciniza. palawpes tu ku hulic nu Payeluse, amana pacakat tulu ku mamikuwan tu Cungtung. sisa mamikuwan ciniza limaay a Cungtung. u Wukelan a tademaw ciniza. u ngangan niza u sulit nu Hulam: 亞歷山大·格里戈里耶維奇·盧卡申科 u sulit nu u sulit nu 羅馬話: Aliaksándar Ryhóravič Lukašénka u sulit nu Amilika: Aleksandr Grigoryevich Lukashenko kakuniza u nasulitan nu Hulam atu Amilika Aleksandr Grigoryevich Lukashenko is the President of Belarus, having been in office since 20 July 1994.Before his career as a politician, Lukashenko worked as director of a state-owned agricultural farm and spent time with the Soviet Border Troops and the Soviet Army. He was the only deputy to vote against the independence of Belarus from the Soviet Union.

== Alexander Lokashenko == o siwkay niza 8 bolad 30 demiad, Alexander Lokashenko, o misingkiway. 1954 a mihca nalecohan o tabakiay a tapang(Congtong) no kanatal (congtong) no Belaros ayza sa ci Alexander Lokashenko, micakat a demiad sa i 1994 a mihca 7 bolad 20 demiad. o tatama, i 1994.7 sakacacay maala ko Congtong ciniza. 2001.9 maala aca ko Congtong ciniza. palawpes to ko holic no Payelose, amana pacakat tolo ko mamikowan to Congtong. sisa mamikowan ciniza limaay a Congtong. o Wokelan a tademaw ciniza. o ngangan niza o solit no Holam: 亞歷山大·格里戈里耶維奇·盧卡申科 o solit no o solit no 羅馬話: Aliaksándar Ryhóravič Lokašénka o solit no Amilika: Aleksandr Grigoryevich Lokashenko kakoniza o nasolitan no Holam ato Amilika Aleksandr Grigoryevich Lokashenko is the President of Belaros, having been in office since 20 Joly 1994.Before his career as a politician, Lokashenko worked as director of a state-owned agricoltoral farm and spent time with the Soviet Border Troops and the Soviet Army. He was the only depoty to vote against the independence of Belaros from the Soviet Union.
